      "children": [
        {
          "text": "8.2. Refresher Training"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "64a2cfef-5905-43be-9986-93ac46f7e1c0",
      "type": "p",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "Conduct annual refresher training or when significant updates are made. Maintain training records for audit and compliance purposes."
